{"tid":974536,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士服務調查報告 45建議採納36項 中環深水埗劃區 車速限30公里","createTime":"2019-01-09T03:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T03:20:28.000Z","uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b375c95631d5ab2540ce3b1867c4dc3377ed4b16","tid":974536,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"會唔會影響交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去年2月大埔公路19死九巴車禍發生距今近一年，政府昨日公布專營巴士服務獨立檢討委員會的調查報告，報告直指運輸署「欠缺長遠、審慎和積極主動對策監管巴士安全」。委員會向政府提出45項建議，政府暫採納36項（部分見圖），包括在行人繁忙地區劃為車輛時速30公里限速區，暫定今年內在深水埗及中環選定街道試行。至於委員會提出將恐嚇辱罵侮辱車長的言行定為罪行，運房局稱目前已有相關法例，故其建議需再研究。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20190109/s00001/1546972264892/%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-45%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%8E%A1%E7%B4%8D36%E9%A0%85-%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%B7%B1%E6%B0%B4%E5%9F%97%E5%8A%83%E5%8D%80-%E8%BB%8A%E9%80%9F%E9%99%9030%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1546972264892%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-45%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%258E%25A1%25E7%25B4%258D36%25E9%25A0%2585-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259F%2597%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%258D%2580-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2599%259030%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2587%258C&d=WIb3OhKSmvf3RGtiUmTrWAIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=85f34dd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190109%2Fs00001%2F1546972264892%2F%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-45%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%258E%25A1%25E7%25B4%258D36%25E9%25A0%2585-%25E4%25B8%25AD